Gurky's Corners neexistuje.

349
00:23:31,093 --> 00:23:33,721
To by máma koukala,
kdyby to slyšela.

350
00:23:33,895 --> 00:23:35,624
Já se tam narodila.

351
00:23:35,831 --> 00:23:38,493
Narodila?

352
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:41,362
Tak, okamžik.

353
00:23:45,373 --> 00:23:48,171
Promiňte,
tohle jsem neotevřel 15 let.

354
00:23:48,343 --> 00:23:52,040
Gurky's Corners. Gurky's Corners.

